 Coulomb interaction, and propose various experimental tools to\ndetermine the underlying ordered states.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 8 Nov 2012 02:26:49 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 12 Jul 2013 19:56:49 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 16 Sep 2013 20:00:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-09-18"}
